// Da luoc bo categories/address trong so do C; chi giu assets, warehouses va warehouse_asset lam ngu canh truc tiep cho giao dich.
// assets.category_id va warehouses.address_id van la field that trong DB; categories/address khong ve o so do C de giu gon.
